title: 2014 SPY DEL MOTO DERBY AT DEL MAR
description:
Happily join SPY for the third annual, Del Moto Derby, Sunday June 8, at the San Diego County Fair.

Where the dirt meets the surf, welcome to the most unique MX event on the West Coast. THIS EVENT IS INVITATION ONLY. 

EVENT INFORMATION
• Sunday, June 8, 2014 @ the Del Mar Fairgrounds
• Motocross, Mini Bike Supercross, Best Whip Contest, Mini Truck Exhibition Race, Track Walk, Autograph Session
• Motocross classes are limited to 24 invited riders: 65cc, Super mini's, Open Intermediate and Pro 
• Main event time is 4 -- 6 pm
• $6,000 purse up for grabs in Pro race
• $1,000 for Best Whip 
• Free admission to the race with ticket to the San Diego County Fair
